search_results.title: Takayuki Tatsumi
search_results.snippet: Takayuki Tatsumi is a Japanese scholar. He is a professor at Keio University, where he has taught literary theory and American literature since 1989.

search_results.title: Headmaster's Voice
search_results.snippet: Biography: Takayuki Tatsumi (1955-) is Professor Emeritus of Keio University, Tokyo, Japan and headmaster of Keio Academy of New York (2022-).
